read_temperature_map_file(25.10)              read_temperature_map_file(25.10)

Name
       read_temperature_map_file  -  Loads the tile-based temperature map file
       generated by Sigrity Celsius to be used for displaying temperature

Syntax
        read_temperature_map_file

       [-help]

       -file <string>

       Loads the tile-based temperature map file generated by Sigrity  Celsius
       to be used for displaying temperature.

Parameters
       -help  Outputs the command usage and a brief description about the com-
              mand parameters.

       -file <string>
              Specifies the name of the tile-based temperature map file gener-
              ated by Sigrity Celsius.

